174 A.3d 508 NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. S.L., DEFENDANT-PETITIONER, AND L.M., DEFENDANT. IN THE MATTER OF M.A.M.-L., A MINOR, RESPONDENT.

C-166 September Term 2017

079258 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000159-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
